sequenceDiagram
    actor User as Developer<br>(Phone)
    participant TG as Telegram API
    participant BOT as ralph-telegram<br>Bot + Handler
    participant STATE as Bot State<br>telegram-state.json
    participant BUS as Event Bus
    participant EL as Event Loop
    participant AGENT as AI Agent<br>(Claude/Kiro/Gemini)

    Note over User,AGENT: Command: /build feature-auth

    User->>TG: /build feature-auth
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>STATE: Store chat_id, command
    BOT->>BUS: Publish human.guidance
    BUS->>EL: Guidance event

    EL->>EL: Inject ROBOT GUIDANCE<br>into next prompt
    EL->>AGENT: Execute with hat + guidance

    AGENT->>AGENT: Plan and implement

    Note over AGENT,User: Agent needs clarification

    AGENT->>BUS: Emit human.interact
    BUS->>EL: Interaction event
    EL->>EL: Block loop
    EL->>BOT: Send question
    BOT->>TG: sendMessage(chat_id, question)
    TG->>User: Display question

    User->>TG: Reply with answer
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>STATE: Match to pending question
    BOT->>BUS: Publish human.response
    BUS->>EL: Response event
    EL->>EL: Unblock loop

    EL->>AGENT: Continue with response

    AGENT->>AGENT: Complete implementation
    AGENT->>BUS: Emit code.complete

    Note over User,AGENT: Command: /status

    User->>TG: /status
    TG->>BOT: Update received
    BOT->>EL: Query current state
    EL-->>BOT: Iteration 7, hat: reviewer
    BOT->>TG: sendMessage(chat_id, status)
    TG->>User: Display status report

    Note over BOT: Retry: 3 attempts<br>exponential backoff<br>on send failure
